"A.P.241/10/20/11:00": "The results of your medical exam came in. There was nothing abnormal that we can see at this time."
"When I heard that you took on [Elder]'s form, I was rather nervous about that ordeal. However, seeing these numbers here have reassured my faith."
"I'm also glad to hear that you also used the Darker Factor as well."
"Well then, if we're able to analyze the mechanism, we'll be able to use it for other purposes as well, if possible..."
"That said, it's still unclear to which you've gained this new ability."
"We still don't know how either..."
"How about this... We'll just continue to monitor this new ability and let's talk about the situation regarding Omega."
"If we take the report at face value, it was mostly a solo operation that lead to the sacking of an emperor."
"And while I say this as if I'm not serious, isn't that normally a tough thing to do? Am I missing something here?"
"No, you're right Alma. Except <%me> isn't exactly normal."
"T-That's not true! <%me> is a normal person!"
"By the way Matoi, you're also not exactly normal."
"How mean! But in that case, isn't Alma..."
"I'm not very good at combat. Claris Claes however, was very good at that."
"Sealing [Elder] away on a planet isn't exactly normal either... Was that still Claris Claes?"
"Nope, that was all me. Even if we had defeated him, he'd just come back again. There was no choice but to seal him away."
"Though, because it was a sudden idea, I think we did pretty okay for that."
"So with that... We can say all of you, are far from normal."
"So with that out of the way, what's the scoop on the Black Hole since we've left?"
"The rate of the Black Hole's expansion has eased up since the time of your report."
"Yep, it's made extracting you two out easier than before."
"It's had an effect on both a mathematical and intuitive perspective."
"Alright... If we keep up the pace while we're in Omega, then I'm sure it'll get better!"
"Easy you two. While I'm sure that you're excited to keep up the good work, don't strain yourselves out there..."
"1. Is there something wrong?"
"2. You're not straining yourself either, right Matoi?"
"I'm alright, but I don't know how to put this into words... But, there's something on my mind."
"It's not from overworking myself, but there's something on my mind."
"While I'm manipulating Photons with Alma, I can feel something out there..."
"An odd feeling, something unlike everyone and Darkers. It's rather strange, it feels like I am being used in some weird way."
"Neither I, nor Xiao would know anything about that, unfortunately..."
"However, there must be something out there for Second to feel that way. Something that we cannot imagine as of yet."
"The sudden appearance of Falz Hunar was unexpected. As well as <%me> using the powers of a Dark Falz."
"Everyone, please be careful out there... If you were to be defeated, then we lose everything."
"Yes, and if you push yourselves too hard, then Second here will faint from worrying herself out."
"Ha, haha... I doubt we'd get that far."
"That said... Please be careful."
"The Rebellion to Elder"
"Suicidal Rebellion"
